==Chinese==

===[[wikipedia:Taiwanese Mandarin|Taiwanese Mandarin]]===
*[[Pinyin]]: Jīanhùgōng 

===Noun===
'''[[監]][[護]][[工]]'''

# A [[caretaker]], an [[in-house nurse]].  A job to take care of a disabled person's eating, moving, bathing, etc..  (Note: In Taiwan, the certificate required to be a nurse is higher than that required to be a "in-house nurse")

===Alternative forms===
* [[监护工]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*看護工
*照顧服務員

